snippet.title: NUTS  - TRAILER (Apple Arcade/Switch/Steam/Itch.io/Humble)
snippet.description:
Gear up your caravan, boot up your GPS, spread out your map and head for the depths of Melmoth Forest. Available on Apple Arcade on Jan 22nd and Nintendo Switch, Steam and Itch.io on Feb 4th.
http://nuts.game



Apple Arcade - https://apple.co/nuts
Nintendo Switch - https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/nuts-switch/
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/768450/NUTS/

Itch.io - https://noodlecake.itch.io/nuts
Humble Store - https://www.humblebundle.com/store/nuts

As a rookie field researcher, you’ll place cameras during the day, and watch the footage at night, tracking the movements of a scurry of squirrels.
Where do they hide their nuts? What puzzling routes do they take? And why do they behave so strangely?
